                                        <title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT4691Prayer#Wednesday">Prayer for the weekdays, Prayer for Wednesday</title>
                                        <incipit xml:lang="gez">
                                            ጸሎት፡ ዘዕለተ፡ ረቡዕ፡ ይትባረክ፡ እግዚአብሔር፡ አቡሁ፡ ለእግዚእነ፡ ኢየሱስ፡ ክርስቶስ፡
                                            አአኵቶ፡ በኵሉ፡ ሰዓት፡ በእንተ፡ ኵሉ፡ ጸጋ፡ ዘወሀበኒ፡ ኅቡዓ፡ ወክሡተ፡
                                        </incipit>
                                    </msItem>
                                    
                                    <msItem xml:id="ms_i3.4.2">
                                        <locus from="106ra" to="107ra"/>
                                        <title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT7316MTReign">Miracle of the Trinity: The future reign of the Trinity</title>
                                        <incipit xml:lang="gez">
                                            ተአምራቲሆሙ፡ <gap reason="ellipsis"/><cb n="b"/><gap reason="ellipsis"/>
                                            ወአሐተ፡ ዕለተ፡ አተዉ፡ ውስተ፡ ገጸ፡ አርያም፡ ይቤ፡ አብኒ፡ ሀለወኒ፡ ጊዜ፡ ይመጽእ፡ 
                                            ቃልየ፡ ወይትሌዓል፡ በ፬ ማዕዘናት፡
                                        </incipit>
                                    </msItem>
                                </msItem>
                                
                                <msItem xml:id="ms_i3.5">
                                    <locus from="107rb" to="115va"/>
                                    <title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT7331SaySelColl#Thursday">Sayfa Śǝllāse-type collection, Thursday</title>
                                    
                                    <msItem xml:id="ms_i3.5.1">
                                        <locus from="107rb" to="115ra"/>
                                        <title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT4691Prayer#Thursday">Prayer for the weekdays, Prayer for Thursday</title>
                                        <incipit xml:lang="gez">
                                            ጸሎት፡ ዘዕለተ፡ ሐሙስ፡ እሴብሖ፡ ለአግዚአብሔር፡ በእንተ፡ ጸጋ፡ ዘወሀበኒ፡ ወዘአፈድፈደ፡ ላእሌየ፡ 
                                            ሠናይቶ፡ ወበረከታቲሁ፡ እለ፡ አልቦን፡ ኍልቍ፡
                                        </incipit>
                                    </msItem>
                                    
                                    <msItem xml:id="ms_i3.5.2">
                                        <locus from="115ra" to="115va"/>
                                        <title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT7312MTBeer">Miracle of the Trinity: Demons burnt in beer</title>
                                        <incipit xml:lang="gez">
                                            ተአምራቲሆሙ፡ <gap reason="ellipsis"/> ወሀሎ፡ ፩ ብእሲ፡ ውስተ፡ ሀገ<cb n="b"/>ረ፡
                                            ፍልስጥኤም፡ ወረሰየ፡ ምዝረ፡ በስመ፡ ሥላሴ፡  ለገቢረ፡ ተዝካሮሙ፡ ወመጽኡ፡ ብዙኃን፡ ሰይጣናት፡ ተመሲሎሙ፡
                                            ከመ፡ አጽልልት፡ ወአተዉ፡ ውስተ፡ ምዝር፡
                                        </incipit>
                                    </msItem>
                                </msItem>
                                
                                <msItem xml:id="ms_i3.6">
                                    <locus from="115vb" to="126ra"/>
                                    <title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT7331SaySelColl#Friday">Sayfa Śǝllāse-type collection, Friday</title>
                                    
                                    <msItem xml:id="ms_i3.6.1">
                                        <locus from="115vb" to="124vb"/>
                                        <title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT7331SaySelColl#PrayerLala">Sayfa Śǝllāse-type collection, div PrayerLala</title>
                                        <note>The text of the prayer for Friday seems to be different from the one
                                            transmitted in <ref type="mss" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/BAVet97">Vatican City, Biblioteca Apostolica Vaticana, Aeth. 97</ref>.</note>
                                        <incipit xml:lang="gez">
                                            ጸሎት፡ ዘዕለተ፡ ዓርብ፡ ላዕለ፡ እግዚአብሔር፡ ተወከልኩ፡ አምላከ፡ አብርሃም፡ ይስሐቅ፡ ወያዕቆብ፡
                                        </incipit>
